description: Outline planning application (all matters reserved with the exception of access) for the redevelopment and master planning of a residential-led development of Phases 5-8 (inclusive) of the Woodberry Down Estate for up to 3,083 homes (C3 Use Class), up to 950m2 Non Residential Uses (F2 'Local Community Use' Use Class) and up to 300m2 Energy Centre (Sui Generis), This is to also include associated landscaping, open space, play provision, public realm and servicing. (THIS APPLICATION IS ACCOMPANIED BY AN ENVIRONMENTAL STATEMENT)
